WEBVTT

00:14.460 --> 00:18.210
[2015]

00:18.240 --> 00:21.500
[Binjiang Province Guhua Prison]

00:29.640 --> 00:30.190
Boss.

00:31.710 --> 00:32.640
Good one.

00:34.070 --> 00:35.330
You've suffered a lot.

00:38.840 --> 00:40.370
Let me light you a cigarette

00:40.430 --> 00:41.470
to get rid of the bad luck.

00:41.470 --> 00:42.400
Thank you, Boss.

00:56.110 --> 00:56.600
Boss,

00:56.870 --> 00:59.070
I need to take care of
something personal first.

00:59.070 --> 00:59.600
Go ahead.

01:13.789 --> 01:14.350
Go home.

01:16.430 --> 01:18.289
Your parents are waiting for you.

01:19.580 --> 01:22.000
[Zhou Jin's father, Zhou Songyue]
[Zhou Jin's mother, Lin Qiuyun]

01:24.150 --> 01:25.640
There's nothing to wait for.

01:25.640 --> 01:26.360
Hurry back.

01:26.640 --> 01:27.370
Jiang Cheng,

01:29.000 --> 01:30.730
I'm giving you one last chance.

01:32.430 --> 01:33.960
Would you come back with me,

01:34.950 --> 01:35.810
or go with them?

01:36.500 --> 01:37.140
Cheng,

01:37.640 --> 01:38.310
who is she?

01:38.440 --> 01:39.640
Just take her with us.

01:44.070 --> 01:45.800
Jiang Cheng, come back with me!

01:47.000 --> 01:47.530
Get lost!

01:48.070 --> 01:49.270
How pathetic are you?

01:57.120 --> 01:58.580
Jiang Cheng, you bastard!

02:00.870 --> 02:02.120
Get up.

02:02.120 --> 02:02.980
Get up quickly.

02:04.790 --> 02:05.400
Are you alright?

02:05.400 --> 02:06.000
I'm fine.

02:08.210 --> 02:09.669
Jiang Cheng, you bastard!

03:32.270 --> 03:38.160
[Sunsets Secrets Regrets]

03:38.510 --> 03:40.920
[Episode 3]

03:43.840 --> 03:45.360
I really don't know
if Meng Ling and Lai San

03:45.360 --> 03:46.360
have any beef.

03:47.400 --> 03:48.590
But if you're asking

03:48.590 --> 03:50.310
who has the biggest grudge
against Lai San around here,

03:50.310 --> 03:51.680
that would definitely be me.

03:51.680 --> 03:53.560
So whether he was threatened or not,

03:53.560 --> 03:55.220
he probably wouldn't tell me.

03:55.420 --> 03:57.280
What's the issue between you two?

03:58.240 --> 03:59.750
He disgusted me,

03:59.800 --> 04:00.750
so I beat him up.

04:01.010 --> 04:02.540
Does that count as a grudge?

04:04.400 --> 04:05.150
To be honest,

04:05.150 --> 04:06.910
you're really asking the wrong person.

04:06.910 --> 04:08.470
I just returned to Haizhou

04:08.470 --> 04:09.270
two weeks ago.

04:09.310 --> 04:11.640
I know nothing about what's going on here.

04:11.750 --> 04:12.470
You've taken

04:12.470 --> 04:13.590
who you wanted.

04:14.030 --> 04:15.240
My place just opened,

04:15.360 --> 04:17.310
and a bunch of buddies are relying on me.

04:17.310 --> 04:18.269
If we keep holding things up,

04:18.269 --> 04:19.130
don't you think

04:19.510 --> 04:21.440
it's getting a bit inappropriate?

04:21.800 --> 04:23.160
Just try to think back a little.

04:23.160 --> 04:26.180
Where were you from July 23

04:26.630 --> 04:27.630
until the early hours of July 24?

04:27.630 --> 04:29.240
I spent the night here.

04:29.350 --> 04:30.880
Anyone who can verify that?

04:31.120 --> 04:32.890
Everyone here can confirm it.

04:33.310 --> 04:33.950
Of course.

04:34.040 --> 04:35.480
If you don't believe me,

04:35.480 --> 04:36.000
look,

04:36.020 --> 04:37.560
all these surveillance cameras

04:37.560 --> 04:38.310
can prove it.

04:38.890 --> 04:40.550
Now you should believe me, right?

04:40.550 --> 04:41.070
Sir.

04:42.780 --> 04:43.830
We'll review

04:44.220 --> 04:46.060
every piece of surveillance carefully.

04:46.060 --> 04:47.450
If you're leading the investigation,

04:47.450 --> 04:48.710
I'll fully cooperate.

04:50.409 --> 04:51.210
Alright then.

04:51.320 --> 04:52.580
Let's leave it at that.

04:53.510 --> 04:54.120
By the way,

04:55.190 --> 04:55.990
don't forget—

04:56.480 --> 04:57.340
stay in Haizhou

04:57.920 --> 04:58.840
for now.

04:59.220 --> 05:00.120
I'll be right here,

05:00.120 --> 05:01.720
ready to assist you anytime.

05:01.750 --> 05:02.350
Very good.

05:03.720 --> 05:04.240
Zhao.

05:04.560 --> 05:04.880
Yes.

05:05.270 --> 05:05.800
Let's go.

05:05.820 --> 05:06.310
Yes.

05:22.040 --> 05:22.680
Sir.

05:25.970 --> 05:27.020
This is my report.

05:31.150 --> 05:32.810
I want to check the back alley.

05:33.210 --> 05:34.010
What's wrong?

05:34.310 --> 05:35.710
I still don't understand

05:36.120 --> 05:36.830
why

05:36.830 --> 05:40.030
Lai Zhengtian knew
police were following him yesterday.

05:41.620 --> 05:42.220
Zhao Ping.

05:44.680 --> 05:45.280
Chief Tan.

05:46.240 --> 05:48.190
Go with your senior
to check the back alley.

05:48.190 --> 05:48.600
Yes.

05:48.730 --> 05:49.260
Go ahead.

06:00.390 --> 06:00.920
Cheng,

06:01.010 --> 06:02.610
let me propose a toast to you.

06:09.760 --> 06:11.590
Officer Zhou, can't bear to leave me?

06:11.590 --> 06:13.580
You just left and now you're back again.

06:13.580 --> 06:14.580
Working on a case.

06:15.040 --> 06:15.920
Need my help?

06:16.180 --> 06:16.910
No need.

07:22.360 --> 07:22.870
Senior!

07:24.410 --> 07:26.060
The weather is so unpredictable.

07:26.060 --> 07:27.920
It starts raining out of nowhere.

07:29.560 --> 07:31.160
What are you thinking about?

07:32.550 --> 07:33.950
There are police indeed.

07:38.390 --> 07:39.030
"Indeed."

07:41.800 --> 07:42.560
Lai,

07:42.830 --> 07:44.150
there are cops here.

07:47.980 --> 07:48.830
Out on duty?

07:50.750 --> 07:53.010
I know police tactics better than you do.

07:57.040 --> 07:58.430
I've thought of a lead,

07:58.760 --> 07:59.890
but I'm not sure yet.

08:00.240 --> 08:01.560
You really have been

08:01.560 --> 08:02.690
badly traumatized.

08:03.100 --> 08:04.670
Not to criticize you, Senior,

08:04.670 --> 08:06.600
but could you stop making us worry?

08:06.900 --> 08:08.200
If it weren't for Professor Jiang
yesterday,

08:08.200 --> 08:10.300
you would've ended up
in the hospital again.

08:10.300 --> 08:12.130
I haven't properly interrogated you yet.

08:12.130 --> 08:13.370
What's going on?

08:13.450 --> 08:15.310
How did you suddenly get married?

08:15.560 --> 08:16.630
Senior, listen.

08:16.970 --> 08:18.530
You never even dated before.

08:18.530 --> 08:20.330
I thought you were afraid of men.

08:20.350 --> 08:22.410
Can you focus on examining the scene?

08:24.050 --> 08:25.370
I am examining it.

08:25.480 --> 08:26.990
Just got carried away talking.

08:26.990 --> 08:28.720
Then keep examining properly.

08:29.630 --> 08:30.870
I'll check if the surveillance footage

08:30.870 --> 08:31.870
has been retrieved.

08:31.870 --> 08:32.270
Okay.

08:33.549 --> 08:34.200
Take the umbrella.

08:34.200 --> 08:34.669
No need.

08:55.480 --> 08:56.540
What are you doing?

08:57.840 --> 08:59.170
Are you dating someone?

09:00.460 --> 09:01.720
None of your business.

09:03.310 --> 09:04.440
Just say you're not.

09:05.040 --> 09:05.770
If you say so,

09:06.270 --> 09:07.270
I'll believe you.

09:08.080 --> 09:08.960
I'm married.

09:13.320 --> 09:13.910
Jin,

09:14.080 --> 09:15.410
you're messing with me.

09:15.760 --> 09:16.750
I'm not.

09:17.650 --> 09:18.780
I'm really married.

09:19.910 --> 09:21.120
He's a good man.

09:22.430 --> 09:23.360
Better than you.

09:31.400 --> 09:33.460
Jiang Cheng, have you lost your mind?

09:50.070 --> 09:51.070
Who did you marry?

09:52.510 --> 09:53.910
That man from last night,

09:54.630 --> 09:55.300
isn't it?

09:59.240 --> 09:59.970
Jiang Cheng,

10:00.920 --> 10:03.180
I really appreciate the life I'm living.

10:04.110 --> 10:05.570
I hope you won't disturb me

10:07.080 --> 10:08.080
and my family.

10:11.600 --> 10:12.240
Family?

10:32.560 --> 10:33.160
By the way,

10:34.320 --> 10:35.120
last night,

10:35.830 --> 10:37.960
it was you who told that person, right?

10:38.370 --> 10:40.170
That the police were following?

11:13.940 --> 11:15.670
You don't need to deny it anymore.

11:15.670 --> 11:16.840
We know exactly

11:16.960 --> 11:18.490
what happened at the scene.

11:21.600 --> 11:22.840
How long have you been doing this?

11:22.840 --> 11:23.970
How did you two meet?

11:25.120 --> 11:26.380
We met while drinking.

11:26.740 --> 11:29.220
But I really liked him.

11:29.960 --> 11:32.220
Did you know Jiang Cheng had drugs on him?

11:32.510 --> 11:33.320
No way.

11:34.390 --> 11:35.850
Isn't he a police officer?

11:37.770 --> 11:38.500
Jiang Cheng.

11:43.160 --> 11:45.220
I don't believe you would hide drugs.

11:46.550 --> 11:48.280
Is someone trying to frame you?

11:51.030 --> 11:51.890
Say something.

11:55.250 --> 11:56.980
I'll believe whatever you say.

11:58.510 --> 11:59.390
Say something.

12:02.460 --> 12:04.000
Did someone set you up?

12:09.300 --> 12:11.060
When did you become like this?

12:16.070 --> 12:17.710
How could I not know at all?

12:22.740 --> 12:24.140
If there's nothing else,

12:25.060 --> 12:26.720
let's leave it at that for now.

12:48.600 --> 12:51.560
[Deputy Captain of the Criminal Investigation Brigade
of Fengzhou District, Haizhou City, Binjiang Province]

12:56.240 --> 12:57.000
Come in.

13:01.720 --> 13:02.240
Sir,

13:02.270 --> 13:03.400
you wanted to see me?

13:11.000 --> 13:12.260
There's new evidence.

13:12.750 --> 13:13.840
The forensics lab

13:14.750 --> 13:15.960
needs someone to follow up.

13:15.960 --> 13:16.820
Go check it out.

13:17.480 --> 13:18.000
Yes.

13:18.550 --> 13:19.840
Professor Jiang is there too.

13:19.840 --> 13:20.500
From now on,

13:21.030 --> 13:23.830
you'll be responsible
for coordinating with him.

13:28.790 --> 13:30.190
Is there something else?

13:33.540 --> 13:34.420
Sir...

13:36.750 --> 13:38.020
There's something

13:39.320 --> 13:40.780
I need to inform you about.

13:42.120 --> 13:42.650
Go ahead.

13:45.680 --> 13:46.700
Phoenix Fire...

13:50.120 --> 13:51.850
Jiang Cheng from Phoenix Fire…

13:53.550 --> 13:54.840
He…

13:58.030 --> 13:59.770
He was my…

14:03.710 --> 14:04.920
My ex.

14:05.270 --> 14:06.000
Boyfriend.

14:06.220 --> 14:06.630
No,

14:06.660 --> 14:07.470
ex-boyfriend.

14:07.470 --> 14:08.540
Ex-boyfriend.

14:09.720 --> 14:10.850
So you already knew?

14:11.510 --> 14:12.510
I was just waiting

14:13.120 --> 14:14.720
to see when you'd tell me.

14:16.000 --> 14:16.600
Sir,

14:17.080 --> 14:19.060
I have absolutely no relationship
with him now.

14:19.060 --> 14:20.120
I promise his presence

14:20.120 --> 14:21.480
won't affect my work at all.

14:21.480 --> 14:22.690
Yes, you don't need to be so nervous.

14:22.690 --> 14:23.890
No one is blaming you.

14:25.420 --> 14:26.030
Actually,

14:26.910 --> 14:28.070
that day in the storage room,

14:28.070 --> 14:29.910
he was the one who led the attack.

14:34.270 --> 14:35.480
Working under He Wu

14:35.480 --> 14:37.010
and reaching his position,

14:38.550 --> 14:40.480
he can't be a good person.

14:41.550 --> 14:42.750
And I've noticed

14:43.080 --> 14:44.540
that the way he looks at you

14:46.630 --> 14:47.750
isn't pure.

14:48.240 --> 14:48.790
So,

14:49.360 --> 14:50.480
from now on,

14:51.270 --> 14:53.530
you should go to Phoenix Fire less often.

14:54.150 --> 14:54.550
Okay.

14:55.150 --> 14:55.950
You can go now.

15:32.270 --> 15:33.270
Professor Jiang.

15:36.360 --> 15:37.160
What's wrong?

15:37.240 --> 15:37.770
Nothing.

15:39.120 --> 15:39.980
Have you eaten?

15:40.510 --> 15:41.370
I'm not hungry.

15:42.840 --> 15:43.970
I haven't eaten yet.

15:44.200 --> 15:45.260
Let's go together.

15:46.200 --> 15:48.600
Didn't you say
there was some new progress?

15:49.870 --> 15:51.870
We need to wait for the results
from the tech department.

15:51.870 --> 15:53.270
We'll have answers soon.

15:55.030 --> 15:56.490
Can you handle spicy food?

15:56.550 --> 15:58.950
There's a good Sichuan restaurant nearby.

15:58.960 --> 16:00.620
We can get takeout from there.

16:00.960 --> 16:01.960
We go there often.

16:02.560 --> 16:03.890
I'm fine with anything.

16:04.320 --> 16:04.670
Okay.

16:09.960 --> 16:10.630
Dan,

16:10.960 --> 16:11.930
do you want some Sichuan food?

16:11.930 --> 16:13.200
I can bring you some takeout.

16:13.200 --> 16:14.670
There are quite a few people today.

16:14.670 --> 16:16.030
About eight or nine people.

16:16.030 --> 16:16.790
No problem.

16:16.840 --> 16:18.370
Someone's treating today.

16:18.390 --> 16:20.910
I know who's paying.

16:21.120 --> 16:22.140
Nine portions in total.

16:22.140 --> 16:23.320
Thank you for your kindness.

16:23.320 --> 16:24.920
Thank you, Professor Jiang.

16:25.000 --> 16:25.600
Just wait.

16:33.360 --> 16:33.890
Let's go.

16:34.870 --> 16:35.400
Zhou Jin.

16:37.080 --> 16:37.880
What's wrong?

16:38.480 --> 16:39.510
You lost a button.

16:55.200 --> 16:57.000
I don't even know how it fell off.

17:02.530 --> 17:03.990
Be more careful next time.

17:15.750 --> 17:16.480
Right there!

17:16.790 --> 17:17.720
That's perfect!

17:18.730 --> 17:21.440
A-After you finish massaging my back,

17:21.730 --> 17:23.260
please massage my head too.

17:23.720 --> 17:26.380
My head hurts
from drinking too much yesterday.

17:44.310 --> 17:44.840
Brother,

17:45.750 --> 17:46.210
it's me.

18:01.070 --> 18:03.310
Jiang Cheng, are you crazy?

18:03.550 --> 18:04.610
What are you doing?

18:05.970 --> 18:07.370
I'm here to take someone.

18:08.350 --> 18:09.190
I'm taking Da Mao

18:09.190 --> 18:10.040
with me.

18:10.790 --> 18:13.310
He's Lai's man.
What right do you have to take him?

18:13.310 --> 18:14.880
Lai San is about to get shot,

18:14.880 --> 18:16.530
yet you're still showing off?

18:16.530 --> 18:18.680
From now on, what I say goes.

18:18.720 --> 18:19.850
Don't waste my time!

18:21.210 --> 18:22.450
He's blind anyway.

18:22.720 --> 18:23.850
What use is he to you?

18:27.260 --> 18:28.800
You're the one who blinded him!

18:28.800 --> 18:29.730
Well, that's...

18:34.800 --> 18:35.400
Cheng,

18:37.200 --> 18:39.260
I respect that you've come out on top.

18:41.480 --> 18:42.960
Let's cut the crap.

18:43.590 --> 18:44.880
I won't hold it against you

18:44.880 --> 18:46.120
about what happened a year ago.

18:46.120 --> 18:47.250
I'm taking him with me.

18:47.250 --> 18:50.450
If you want to blame someone,
blame Lai for being useless.

18:52.960 --> 18:54.000
Count it.

18:54.200 --> 18:56.130
Don't say I don't follow the rules.

18:56.550 --> 18:57.080
Xiao Mao,

18:57.400 --> 18:58.730
take your brother home.

19:06.560 --> 19:07.560
This is the place.

19:15.790 --> 19:16.270
Zhang.

19:17.310 --> 19:18.840
Officer Zhou, you're here.

19:19.000 --> 19:20.460
What would you like today?

19:20.720 --> 19:21.350
The usual.

19:21.550 --> 19:24.030
Two meat and two vegetable dishes,
nine portions. Deliver them to the team.

19:24.030 --> 19:25.180
Then bring the menu over.

19:25.180 --> 19:25.880
We're eating here.

19:25.880 --> 19:26.440
Alright.

19:27.720 --> 19:28.720
Take a look first.

19:34.750 --> 19:35.750
Professor Jiang.

19:36.440 --> 19:37.880
If my habit is

19:38.480 --> 19:39.680
to order four dishes,

19:40.000 --> 19:41.800
split them into three portions,

19:41.890 --> 19:43.550
and eat them over three meals,

19:43.920 --> 19:44.780
would you mind?

19:46.270 --> 19:46.800
Zhou Jin.

19:47.640 --> 19:48.770
My salary is decent.

19:49.190 --> 19:50.110
You don't need to be so frugal.

19:50.110 --> 19:51.400
It's not about saving money.

19:51.400 --> 19:53.130
I just don't want to waste food.

19:53.960 --> 19:55.000
Can we discuss this?

19:55.000 --> 19:56.110
Of course we can.

19:56.550 --> 19:58.440
You're the godsend to our team.

19:58.750 --> 20:01.150
Even Sir
keeps talking about you every day.

20:01.310 --> 20:03.200
So I need to make sure
you're properly settled in.

20:03.200 --> 20:04.220
Food is the first necessity of the people.

20:04.220 --> 20:05.550
And you are my priority.

20:05.750 --> 20:08.170
I think ordering three dishes
would be just right.

20:08.170 --> 20:09.430
I have a good appetite.

20:09.750 --> 20:10.350
Zhou Jin,

20:11.200 --> 20:12.460
there are two of us now.

20:15.350 --> 20:15.880
Okay.

20:46.710 --> 20:48.310
Here's the Kung Pao Chicken!

20:49.560 --> 20:50.360
Officer Zhou,

20:50.590 --> 20:51.590
you're here.

20:51.720 --> 20:53.920
Where are the other officers
from your team?

20:53.920 --> 20:54.920
They're all busy.

20:55.480 --> 20:57.480
So you've officially started working?

20:57.480 --> 20:58.880
How have you been lately?

21:02.790 --> 21:04.000
I've really quit.

21:04.400 --> 21:05.270
Officer Zhou,

21:05.510 --> 21:06.240
don't worry.

21:06.440 --> 21:07.700
I don't have any cravings at all.

21:07.700 --> 21:08.430
That's good.

21:08.480 --> 21:10.080
You look much healthier now.

21:10.160 --> 21:12.090
And you have a good complexion too.

21:12.200 --> 21:14.510
This officer looks unfamiliar.

21:14.590 --> 21:16.070
I haven't seen him before, right?

21:16.070 --> 21:16.920
This is...

21:17.510 --> 21:18.440
He is...

21:19.510 --> 21:21.370
He's Professor Jiang, a teacher.

21:22.400 --> 21:24.660
I see. Nice to meet you, Professor Jiang.

21:24.670 --> 21:25.550
Nice to meet you.

21:25.550 --> 21:27.530
I'll ask the kitchen
to prepare a Sichuan Boiled Fish.

21:27.530 --> 21:28.860
Have some before you go.

21:29.680 --> 21:32.240
No need. Officer Zhou
is sensitive to fishy smells.

21:32.240 --> 21:33.350
She doesn't like fish.

21:33.350 --> 21:34.670
Alright then, take your time and chat.

21:34.670 --> 21:36.400
I'll go back to the kitchen now.

21:39.030 --> 21:41.630
How did you know
I'm sensitive to fishy smells?

21:52.270 --> 21:53.640
Bai Yang, what's up?

21:54.110 --> 21:55.550
Is Professor Jiang with you?

21:55.550 --> 21:56.150
Yes, he is.

21:56.680 --> 21:58.740
Tell him he's absolutely brilliant.

21:58.830 --> 21:59.880
Following his instructions,

21:59.880 --> 22:01.750
I checked all the ride-hailing services
and illegal taxis

22:01.750 --> 22:03.200
that passed through Tonghe riverside
and used the Haiji Highway

22:03.200 --> 22:04.350
around the time of the incident.

22:04.350 --> 22:05.440
Haiji Highway?

22:05.830 --> 22:06.630
That's right.

22:06.880 --> 22:08.550
Honglian County is Meng Ling's hometown.

22:08.550 --> 22:10.920
If Meng Ling wanted
to return to Honglian from Haizhou,

22:10.920 --> 22:11.750
then the Haiji Highway

22:11.750 --> 22:13.610
would be the route she had to take.

22:14.070 --> 22:15.720
So she booked a ride in advance

22:15.720 --> 22:16.980
but never made it home.

22:17.070 --> 22:18.270
Yes, very likely.

22:18.720 --> 22:21.000
There's a van that operates
as an unlicensed taxi.

22:21.000 --> 22:22.680
It was at the Tonghe riverside
on the night of the incident,

22:22.680 --> 22:25.030
and it frequently travels
between Honglian and Haizhou.

22:25.030 --> 22:26.160
Can we find this van?

22:26.690 --> 22:27.620
It's in the city.

22:28.000 --> 22:29.680
How did you come up with this?

22:30.310 --> 22:31.770
Professor Jiang analyzed

22:31.790 --> 22:33.200
that if Lai San had premeditated

22:33.200 --> 22:34.200
to kill Meng Ling,

22:34.720 --> 22:36.550
he wouldn't have used a standard gun.

22:36.550 --> 22:37.720
Meng Ling was so frail.

22:37.720 --> 22:39.590
He could have used a more common weapon.

22:39.590 --> 22:41.200
And he wouldn't need to do it himself.

22:41.200 --> 22:42.550
Also, from the surveillance footage,

22:42.550 --> 22:43.510
when Meng Ling went to meet someone,

22:43.510 --> 22:45.720
she didn't show any signs of tension
or anxiety.

22:45.720 --> 22:46.550
Lai San's action

22:46.550 --> 22:48.070
was likely a crime of passion.

22:48.070 --> 22:51.530
Meng Ling actually had a real chance
to return to her hometown.

22:52.250 --> 22:54.000
Okay, I'll get Zhao Ping
to track the van.

22:54.000 --> 22:56.260
Send him the license plate and location.

22:56.480 --> 22:57.160
Got it.

23:01.000 --> 23:02.000
Professor Jiang,

23:02.240 --> 23:03.670
Bai Yang did as you said

23:03.830 --> 23:04.680
and found the clue.

23:04.680 --> 23:06.110
So this is the result
you wanted us to wait for,

23:06.110 --> 23:06.790
isn't it?

23:10.240 --> 23:11.840
Bring that person back to me.

23:13.720 --> 23:14.460
When did this idea

23:14.460 --> 23:15.540
first come to you?

23:16.750 --> 23:17.480
Yesterday.

23:18.160 --> 23:19.670
Then why didn't you tell me

23:19.750 --> 23:21.000
when I asked

23:21.350 --> 23:23.550
if you had anything to add this morning?

23:23.550 --> 23:25.750
I wanted to wait
until I had results to tell you.

23:25.750 --> 23:26.880
But we're partners.

23:27.790 --> 23:30.110
Shouldn't partners
tell each other everything?

23:30.110 --> 23:32.310
Even though I'm happy with this result,

23:32.720 --> 23:34.440
I don't like

23:34.880 --> 23:36.480
being kept in the dark

23:36.920 --> 23:37.550
like this.

23:38.510 --> 23:39.710
We're just partners?

23:40.550 --> 23:43.010
You're the expert
and I'm here to assist you.

23:43.020 --> 23:44.190
I can learn from you,

23:44.640 --> 23:45.940
but I need to be kept in the loop

23:45.940 --> 23:47.070
and give my consent.

23:47.310 --> 23:49.040
That's called mutual respect.

23:51.440 --> 23:52.860
I understand what you mean.

23:52.860 --> 23:54.120
It won't happen again.

23:54.310 --> 23:54.910
I'm sorry.

23:56.270 --> 23:56.960
Never mind.

23:57.230 --> 23:58.010
Professor Jiang,

23:58.010 --> 23:59.070
let's keep eating.

24:10.960 --> 24:11.880
Did you choke?

24:16.680 --> 24:17.210
Zhou Jin,

24:18.050 --> 24:19.450
this is really too spicy.

24:20.070 --> 24:20.680
Spicy?

24:21.720 --> 24:23.320
Can't you handle spicy food?

24:24.960 --> 24:26.300
Why didn't you tell me?

24:27.590 --> 24:28.240
I'm sorry.

24:29.270 --> 24:30.400
I'm not blaming you.

24:31.850 --> 24:32.570
I remember

24:33.110 --> 24:33.780
you like it.

24:38.160 --> 24:38.800
Jin,

24:38.830 --> 24:40.090
why aren't you eating?

24:40.250 --> 24:41.620
How could she handle this stuff?

24:41.220 --> 24:43.960
[2002]

24:42.350 --> 24:43.350
She insisted on coming along.

24:43.350 --> 24:44.480
Feeling stupid now?

24:44.760 --> 24:45.620
I can handle it.

24:48.500 --> 24:50.680
Jiang Cheng, look—
Jin got hit by the spice.

24:50.680 --> 24:52.800
Why are you overestimating yourself?

24:52.800 --> 24:54.590
Who said that? I love spicy food.

24:54.590 --> 24:55.510
I just choked earlier,

24:55.510 --> 24:56.440
got it?

24:59.960 --> 25:01.360
I don't like it that much.

25:01.830 --> 25:03.340
We can try
a different restaurant next time.

25:03.340 --> 25:04.100
I'm fine.

25:08.030 --> 25:09.160
But I'm not.

25:10.480 --> 25:11.480
Professor Jiang,

25:12.750 --> 25:14.410
I don't want you to compromise

25:14.440 --> 25:15.770
just to accommodate me.

25:16.310 --> 25:17.750
You can just tell me what you like

25:17.750 --> 25:18.880
and what you don't.

25:19.790 --> 25:20.750
From now on, we'll order things

25:20.750 --> 25:22.070
we both enjoy.

25:24.210 --> 25:25.070
How about this?

25:25.510 --> 25:27.440
Let's order some non-spicy dishes.

25:27.440 --> 25:28.480
I'll take these home

25:28.480 --> 25:29.810
for a late-night snack.

25:30.960 --> 25:31.810
It's up to you.

25:32.640 --> 25:33.970
You're so considerate.

25:38.560 --> 25:40.360
Let your brother have some more.

25:42.700 --> 25:43.590
Slow down.

25:47.310 --> 25:48.480
Eat slowly.

25:49.160 --> 25:50.810
After dinner,
take your brother to the boat.

25:50.810 --> 25:52.230
Once you've settled in
at your destination,

25:52.230 --> 25:53.690
remember to give me a call.

25:54.230 --> 25:55.290
Sure thing, Cheng.

25:58.110 --> 25:59.720
This money is for your brother
to open a shop.

25:59.720 --> 26:00.830
Don't spend it carelessly,

26:00.830 --> 26:02.360
or I'll twist your head off.

26:04.240 --> 26:05.750
Count it yourself when you get there.

26:05.750 --> 26:06.630
There's 50,000 inside.

26:06.630 --> 26:08.110
Don't give any to your younger brother.

26:08.110 --> 26:09.920
Eating is the only thing he's good at.

26:09.920 --> 26:10.680
Alright.

26:12.680 --> 26:13.400
Cheng,

26:13.750 --> 26:14.590
my brother

26:14.660 --> 26:15.720
wants to thank you.

26:17.030 --> 26:17.770
If it weren't for

26:17.770 --> 26:19.630
Boss He sending me away back then,

26:19.720 --> 26:22.250
your brother
wouldn't have suffered so much.

26:22.300 --> 26:24.270
It's all because everything
that bastard Lai San did

26:24.270 --> 26:25.400
was inhuman.

26:26.600 --> 26:29.930
Now that you're back,
everyone will have better days ahead.

26:34.790 --> 26:35.790
By the way, Cheng,

26:36.000 --> 26:38.200
why would Lai San want to kill Meng Ling?

26:38.400 --> 26:39.310
How would I know?

26:39.310 --> 26:40.640
He's crazy, that's why.

26:41.000 --> 26:42.350
But people are saying

26:42.790 --> 26:44.990
that you turned Lai San in to the police.

26:45.070 --> 26:45.880
Nonsense!

26:45.950 --> 26:47.470
Did I tell him to kill that person?

26:47.470 --> 26:48.540
That's impossible.

26:48.540 --> 26:49.170
Cheng,

26:49.390 --> 26:50.250
you don't know,

26:50.890 --> 26:53.890
Meng Ling has had a terrible time
these past two years.

27:05.590 --> 27:07.520
Enough. Let's not talk about this.

27:08.290 --> 27:09.270
Here, Brother.

27:22.400 --> 27:23.600
What's wrong, Cheng?

27:25.960 --> 27:26.760
It's nothing.

27:27.030 --> 27:28.090
Boss He is back now.

27:30.550 --> 27:31.860
So don't worry anymore.

27:31.860 --> 27:34.320
If the sky falls,
he'll be there to hold it up.

27:37.750 --> 27:38.360
What's up?

27:56.360 --> 27:58.160
This is the password?

28:03.200 --> 28:04.530
For Liu Jinlong's safe?

28:06.550 --> 28:07.240
Wait.

28:07.750 --> 28:09.550
Brother, how did you...

28:12.160 --> 28:13.710
So you're half-blind.

28:16.420 --> 28:17.250
Let me do it.

28:45.340 --> 28:46.780
Jiang Cheng.

28:48.510 --> 28:49.900
Cheng.

28:58.680 --> 28:59.940
I heard from Chief Tan.

29:00.040 --> 29:01.380
Lai Zhengtian has been arrested,

29:01.380 --> 29:02.680
but the gun hasn't been found,

29:02.680 --> 29:04.440
and you couldn't get information
about the primary crime scene.

29:04.440 --> 29:04.750
That's true.

29:04.750 --> 29:06.920
We're still looking for a breakthrough,

29:06.920 --> 29:08.960
so we want to understand
the specific situation.

29:08.960 --> 29:10.200
Since the municipal bureau
takes this case seriously,

29:10.200 --> 29:11.200
our cooperation is essential.

29:11.200 --> 29:12.130
That's our duty.

29:12.350 --> 29:13.510
I mainly want to know about

29:13.510 --> 29:14.920
the assault case from a year ago.

29:14.920 --> 29:15.400
Okay,

29:15.550 --> 29:17.270
let's start from the beginning

29:17.270 --> 29:18.330
and go into detail.

29:19.030 --> 29:19.880
I remember

29:19.880 --> 29:22.240
it was the night of June 11th last year

29:22.240 --> 29:23.590
when we received the call.

29:23.590 --> 29:24.720
A resident reported

29:24.830 --> 29:26.480
hearing heart-wrenching screams

29:26.480 --> 29:28.920
near Funing Street;

29:29.410 --> 29:30.110
they were truly horrifying.

29:29.490 --> 29:34.280
[2016]

29:30.960 --> 29:32.030
When they went to check,

29:32.030 --> 29:34.200
four or five people
were beating someone up.

29:34.200 --> 29:34.790
Afraid someone might die,

29:34.790 --> 29:36.720
they called the police right away.

29:41.960 --> 29:43.070
Go to hell!

29:43.720 --> 29:45.220
That's for bullying my sister!

29:45.220 --> 29:46.370
Just kill me!

29:46.400 --> 29:47.200
I'll kill you!

29:47.270 --> 29:48.480
Just kill me!

29:48.500 --> 29:50.390
Stop hitting me!

29:51.110 --> 29:52.820
The place where they fought

29:53.000 --> 29:54.930
was under renovation at that time.

29:55.020 --> 29:55.880
There weren't many people around

29:55.880 --> 29:57.080
and no lights either.

29:57.240 --> 29:58.830
After we received the report,

29:58.830 --> 30:00.830
we arrived at the scene in 10 minutes

30:00.960 --> 30:02.480
and took everyone away.

30:10.270 --> 30:11.000
Are you okay?

30:11.720 --> 30:12.250
I'm fine.

30:12.480 --> 30:14.350
The victim was Lai Zhengtian.

30:14.880 --> 30:17.160
His arm was severely injured,

30:17.440 --> 30:18.550
so he was sent to the hospital.

30:18.550 --> 30:20.680
We interrogated the attackers first.

30:21.310 --> 30:21.720
Yes.

30:22.720 --> 30:25.030
The man who led the fight

30:25.240 --> 30:26.300
has the surname Hu.

30:26.440 --> 30:27.700
He has a younger sister

30:28.030 --> 30:31.310
who attended Guoshan Experimental
High School a few years ago.

30:31.310 --> 30:33.750
One night,
after her evening study session,

30:33.750 --> 30:35.030
she ran into Lai Zhengtian

30:35.030 --> 30:36.590
on her way home.

30:37.510 --> 30:39.110
That scumbag Lai Zhengtian

30:39.510 --> 30:40.880
sexually assaulted

30:41.110 --> 30:41.960
the poor girl.

30:42.680 --> 30:44.070
The girl was terrified

30:44.350 --> 30:45.950
and didn't dare tell anyone.

30:46.290 --> 30:47.210
Until one day,

30:47.240 --> 30:48.480
she had an emotional breakdown

30:48.480 --> 30:49.810
and attempted suicide.

30:49.880 --> 30:51.310
Only then did her family learn

30:51.310 --> 30:52.440
what had happened.

30:53.180 --> 30:54.390
I remember at that time,

30:54.390 --> 30:56.260
he had an arm broken, right?

30:57.000 --> 30:57.830
Left arm.

31:00.720 --> 31:02.580
Maybe it wasn't just the left arm.

31:03.400 --> 31:06.030
Was there something else?

31:07.480 --> 31:08.110
Well...

31:10.790 --> 31:12.350
I want to know every detail.

31:12.860 --> 31:14.260
Thanks for cooperating.

31:17.510 --> 31:19.240
It's not that we can't tell you.

31:19.510 --> 31:20.350
It's just

31:20.920 --> 31:23.750
really hard to talk about.

31:27.720 --> 31:28.720
To put it simply,

31:29.270 --> 31:30.130
they basically

31:30.550 --> 31:31.480
gave him a taste

31:31.880 --> 31:33.010
of his own medicine.

31:36.810 --> 31:37.640
Well,

31:37.680 --> 31:38.790
the girl's brother

31:39.900 --> 31:41.700
used some rather brutal methods

31:41.940 --> 31:43.050
to get revenge.

31:46.080 --> 31:48.200
You're saying Meng Ling knew about this

31:48.200 --> 31:49.330
and mentioned it,

31:49.370 --> 31:51.100
which provoked Lai Zhengtian?

31:51.150 --> 31:52.410
According to our analysis,

31:52.410 --> 31:54.380
Lai Zhengtian
committed a crime of passion.

31:54.380 --> 31:55.640
There must be a reason.

31:56.040 --> 31:58.300
Meng Ling said she had leverage over him.

31:58.920 --> 32:00.380
Could it be this incident?

32:01.230 --> 32:02.090
Lai Zhengtian,

32:02.400 --> 32:04.400
with his cousin He Wu as his backing,

32:04.680 --> 32:06.010
had always been a bully.

32:06.490 --> 32:08.090
He was always the aggressor.

32:08.210 --> 32:09.540
But after that night,

32:09.750 --> 32:11.280
he was not only victimized,

32:11.350 --> 32:13.470
but also couldn't even bring himself
to speak of his suffering.

32:13.470 --> 32:15.630
It was absolutely a profound humiliation.

32:15.630 --> 32:16.270
So that was

32:16.300 --> 32:18.160
a major trauma for Lai Zhengtian.

32:18.510 --> 32:19.220
That's why

32:19.250 --> 32:21.380
he recklessly shot someone.

32:21.590 --> 32:22.640
It's not the only explanation,

32:22.640 --> 32:24.300
but it's significant enough.

32:24.310 --> 32:26.240
And I heard in Hongyun's testimony

32:26.680 --> 32:28.140
that after Jiang Cheng...

32:34.570 --> 32:36.370
After Jiang Cheng left Haizhou,

32:36.560 --> 32:38.270
Lai Zhengtian, out of revenge,

32:38.270 --> 32:39.110
subjected Meng Ling

32:39.110 --> 32:41.280
to various forms of abuse for a long time.

32:41.280 --> 32:41.930
Yes.

32:42.460 --> 32:44.460
From a psychological perspective,

32:44.470 --> 32:46.400
this strong tendency toward abuse

32:46.450 --> 32:48.450
may stem from various motivations,

32:48.610 --> 32:49.470
but typically,

32:49.920 --> 32:52.850
it's about releasing
uncontrollable primal urges.

32:55.860 --> 32:57.790
That person is Jiang Cheng, right?

32:59.050 --> 33:00.510
It was just a chance encounter,

33:00.510 --> 33:02.030
and then

33:02.310 --> 33:04.240
some unpleasant things happened.

33:04.340 --> 33:05.940
I'm heading to Phoenix Fire.

33:06.580 --> 33:07.170
Zhou Jin.

33:08.100 --> 33:09.100
You lost a button.

33:11.960 --> 33:13.760
I don't even know how it fell off.

33:15.750 --> 33:16.680
Jiang Hansheng.

33:19.160 --> 33:20.000
What I mean is,

33:20.770 --> 33:22.870
given Lai Zhengtian's
current physical state

33:22.870 --> 33:24.400
and his past with Meng Ling,

33:24.750 --> 33:26.310
even if he didn't shoot because of this,

33:26.310 --> 33:27.400
it would be enough to break down

33:27.400 --> 33:28.790
his mental defenses.

33:29.110 --> 33:30.390
I agree with your point.

33:30.390 --> 33:32.350
You can try it during the interrogation.

33:32.350 --> 33:32.920
Great!

33:34.220 --> 33:35.170
I'll go try it then.

33:35.170 --> 33:35.780
Zhou Jin,

33:36.240 --> 33:37.990
once Lai Zhengtian mentally breaks down,

33:37.990 --> 33:39.990
he might exhibit extreme behavior.

33:39.990 --> 33:41.650
Let Chief Tan know about this.

33:44.150 --> 33:44.950
I understand.

33:47.720 --> 33:49.320
Are you coming home tonight?

33:49.550 --> 33:50.790
I probably won't make it back.

33:50.790 --> 33:51.640
If it gets late,

33:51.640 --> 33:53.170
I'll sleep in the duty dorm.

33:54.200 --> 33:54.590
Okay.

33:58.070 --> 33:58.680
Zhou Jin.

34:00.640 --> 34:01.240
What is it?

34:02.400 --> 34:03.330
Where did you put

34:03.350 --> 34:04.410
your wedding ring?

34:06.510 --> 34:07.440
It's at my place.

34:09.489 --> 34:11.690
Why are you suddenly asking about this?

34:11.760 --> 34:13.620
Nothing. Carry on with your work.

34:38.469 --> 34:39.350
Where did you go

34:39.370 --> 34:41.370
on the 23rd and 24th?

34:41.400 --> 34:41.920
Who did you meet?

34:41.920 --> 34:42.440
What did you eat?

34:42.440 --> 34:43.360
What did you drink?

34:43.360 --> 34:45.760
You'd better recall everything right now.

34:45.760 --> 34:46.590
We've already found out

34:46.590 --> 34:48.110
you weren't home that day at all.

34:48.110 --> 34:49.370
Tell us where you went.

34:51.670 --> 34:52.530
Lai Zhengtian!

34:53.480 --> 34:54.540
I'm talking to you.

34:56.070 --> 34:57.910
Why so loud? You startled me.

34:58.340 --> 34:59.270
Why don't you guess?

34:59.270 --> 35:01.270
This guy can really drag things out.

35:01.300 --> 35:03.560
If he didn't have grudges with Meng Ling,

35:03.610 --> 35:05.670
I'd wonder if we got the wrong person.

35:07.670 --> 35:09.230
Coffee's here.

35:09.230 --> 35:10.690
Thanks for your hard work.

35:10.840 --> 35:12.230
Thank you.

35:19.800 --> 35:20.530
Thanks, Dan.

35:22.920 --> 35:23.840
Smells good.

35:25.030 --> 35:26.090
Here, take a sniff.

35:30.210 --> 35:32.670
Any new instructions from Professor Jiang?

35:39.800 --> 35:40.660
Actually, yes.

35:42.270 --> 35:42.750
Dan,

35:43.000 --> 35:43.880
come in with me.

35:44.190 --> 35:44.850
In a moment,

35:44.930 --> 35:46.470
I'll handle the questioning,

35:46.470 --> 35:47.930
and you just need to smile.

35:48.000 --> 35:48.510
Smile?

35:49.710 --> 35:51.370
What's that supposed to mean?

35:53.070 --> 35:54.230
I want you

35:54.780 --> 35:55.840
to look down on him.

35:57.060 --> 35:59.060
Show him pure contempt from a woman.

36:06.130 --> 36:06.590
Mr. Wan,

36:06.800 --> 36:08.130
let me take over for you.

36:19.220 --> 36:19.950
Look.

36:20.850 --> 36:22.840
If they had sent you two
to keep me company earlier,

36:22.840 --> 36:24.500
I wouldn't have been so bored.

36:25.380 --> 36:26.290
Maybe

36:26.710 --> 36:27.800
if you cheer me up,

36:27.800 --> 36:29.400
I might remember something.

36:29.890 --> 36:30.880
Do you remember me?

36:30.880 --> 36:31.710
Of course I do.

36:32.570 --> 36:33.500
Absolutely.

36:34.310 --> 36:35.660
You're quite a catch.

36:35.880 --> 36:37.940
Why did you end up in this profession?

36:38.000 --> 36:39.800
If you worked for me,

36:40.070 --> 36:41.130
I would definitely

36:41.510 --> 36:42.550
turn you into

36:42.880 --> 36:44.760
the most famous princess.

36:45.400 --> 36:47.060
So many men would fall for you.

36:47.480 --> 36:48.710
The market right now

36:49.010 --> 36:50.610
is missing someone like you.

36:51.440 --> 36:52.840
Do you know where you are?

36:53.070 --> 36:54.230
No sense of fun.

36:55.440 --> 36:56.590
What type am I?

36:58.840 --> 36:59.900
A little spitfire.

37:00.590 --> 37:02.230
I have a good eye for people.

37:02.710 --> 37:03.550
Look at you,

37:03.960 --> 37:04.900
pretty face,

37:05.610 --> 37:06.540
long neck,

37:06.630 --> 37:07.590
broad shoulders,

37:07.590 --> 37:08.510
tiny waist.

37:08.880 --> 37:10.340
You look best in a uniform.

37:10.840 --> 37:11.840
If you work with me

37:11.840 --> 37:13.100
and learn a few tricks,

37:13.510 --> 37:15.510
you'd have men falling at your feet.

37:16.290 --> 37:17.820
In one night,

37:18.760 --> 37:20.400
you'd make more

37:20.400 --> 37:22.200
than a cop makes in a whole month.

37:22.240 --> 37:23.570
So what you're saying is

37:24.100 --> 37:25.760
all the people working for you

37:26.000 --> 37:27.800
were personally trained by you?

37:28.760 --> 37:30.360
Was Meng Ling one of them too?

37:36.240 --> 37:37.550
I'm very picky.

37:38.840 --> 37:40.370
I'm only interested in you.

37:53.890 --> 37:55.220
What are you looking at?

38:05.880 --> 38:07.280
What are you laughing at?

38:09.590 --> 38:10.880
As police officers,

38:10.920 --> 38:12.120
we investigate cases

38:13.110 --> 38:14.510
over and over again.

38:15.110 --> 38:17.000
We found a case from a year ago.

38:20.400 --> 38:21.230
I heard

38:22.320 --> 38:23.620
you were in the hospital

38:23.620 --> 38:25.140
for a long time back then.

38:25.920 --> 38:26.450
How is it?

38:27.510 --> 38:28.440
Is your left hand

38:29.230 --> 38:30.000
better now?

38:30.420 --> 38:32.750
What does this have to do
with my left hand?

38:41.280 --> 38:42.740
What are you saying to her?

38:43.610 --> 38:45.010
What are you laughing at?

38:47.920 --> 38:48.640
Chief Tan.

38:48.660 --> 38:50.120
What are you saying to her?

38:50.760 --> 38:52.420
Hey, what are you laughing at?

38:53.320 --> 38:55.050
Hey, what are you saying to her?

38:55.070 --> 38:56.760
What is Zhou Jin doing in there?

38:56.760 --> 38:57.420
Get her out.

38:58.030 --> 38:58.630
Chief Tan,

38:59.150 --> 39:00.210
let's wait and see.

39:00.440 --> 39:02.550
Lai Zhengtian has finally started talking.

39:02.550 --> 39:03.680
This is a good start.

39:04.070 --> 39:04.670
Yes.

39:48.480 --> 39:51.210
Let me share some scientific knowledge
with you.

39:51.710 --> 39:53.110
A person's experiences,

39:54.150 --> 39:55.840
especially traumatic ones,

39:56.410 --> 39:57.430
can have a profound impact

39:57.430 --> 39:59.430
on their thought patterns

40:00.030 --> 40:01.620
and behavioral habits.

40:02.030 --> 40:03.440
So what is trauma?

40:04.850 --> 40:05.880
I made notes before.

40:05.880 --> 40:07.210
Let me look it up for you.

40:07.480 --> 40:08.710
It will be helpful for you.

40:08.710 --> 40:10.330
I'm definitely not trying to fool you.

40:10.330 --> 40:11.250
Let me find it.

40:12.670 --> 40:14.070
Here, listen carefully.

40:14.800 --> 40:15.760
Trauma

40:16.280 --> 40:17.540
is generally caused by

40:18.010 --> 40:19.490
external factors

40:19.920 --> 40:21.110
and results in

40:21.400 --> 40:22.860
damage to the body or mind.

40:23.460 --> 40:26.380
It is an automatic physiological

40:26.610 --> 40:29.090
and neurological response
of the individual

40:29.090 --> 40:31.450
to overwhelming events or experiences,

40:31.700 --> 40:32.840
which in turn produces

40:32.840 --> 40:34.240
psychological effects.

40:35.230 --> 40:36.800
Psychological trauma

40:37.590 --> 40:38.650
can be divided into

40:38.920 --> 40:41.520
non-interpersonal and interpersonal types.

40:42.030 --> 40:43.590
Today we'll mainly discuss

40:43.890 --> 40:44.950
interpersonal trauma,

40:44.950 --> 40:46.620
which occurs between people.

40:48.240 --> 40:49.360
For example,

40:50.380 --> 40:51.990
when a loved one dies,

40:52.630 --> 40:54.490
when your girlfriend leaves you,

40:54.920 --> 40:56.990
when your brother betrays you,

40:57.390 --> 40:59.350
when you suffer a violent attack,

40:59.510 --> 41:00.590
or perhaps—

41:07.480 --> 41:09.880
What happened to you a year ago

41:10.930 --> 41:12.980
on Funing Street in Guoshan District?

41:12.980 --> 41:13.730
Wretch!

41:15.120 --> 41:16.910
Don't tell me Meng Ling knows everything

41:16.910 --> 41:18.140
like I do.

41:20.360 --> 41:21.110
My God!

41:21.460 --> 41:22.650
What did she tell you

41:22.850 --> 41:24.090
that made you so angry

41:24.120 --> 41:25.410
and so furious?

41:26.960 --> 41:27.800
Could it be

41:28.360 --> 41:29.480
that she told you

41:30.180 --> 41:31.140
your left hand

41:31.510 --> 41:32.220
is useless?

41:33.670 --> 41:34.670
That you can't use

41:35.150 --> 41:36.480
your left hand anymore?

41:38.400 --> 41:39.230
No.

41:40.510 --> 41:41.390
Oh, I get it.

41:42.360 --> 41:43.400
What she have said

41:43.960 --> 41:46.420
has nothing to do
with your left hand, right?

41:46.630 --> 41:47.630
It must be

41:48.620 --> 41:49.910
something worse.

41:55.660 --> 41:56.210
Lai Zhengtian!

41:56.210 --> 41:57.690
I'm going to kill you!

41:58.110 --> 41:58.960
I'm going to kill you!

41:58.960 --> 41:59.760
Calm down!

41:59.760 --> 42:00.680
Don't just stand there!

42:00.680 --> 42:01.410
Help her out!

42:01.740 --> 42:02.990
I'm going to kill you!

42:03.070 --> 42:04.230
I'm going to kill her!

42:04.230 --> 42:04.880
I'm going to kill her!

42:04.880 --> 42:05.670
You're just talking big.

42:05.670 --> 42:06.710
What can you possibly do to me?

42:06.710 --> 42:07.710
I can kill you.

42:07.710 --> 42:08.570
What would you use to kill me?

42:08.570 --> 42:09.710
I'll shoot you with a gun!

42:09.710 --> 42:10.510
Where did you get the gun?

42:10.510 --> 42:11.190
I—

42:18.880 --> 42:20.670
I was just joking.

42:21.710 --> 42:23.320
You all saw it.

42:24.320 --> 42:26.150
I'm just a cripple.

42:27.070 --> 42:28.960
I can't kill anyone.

42:41.360 --> 42:41.960
Chief Tan,

42:42.550 --> 42:44.350
I'll go organize the materials.

42:49.630 --> 42:50.550
I can see that.

42:52.280 --> 42:54.010
I know what you're trying to do.

42:54.630 --> 42:55.190
Really,

42:55.500 --> 42:56.410
we were so close.

42:56.410 --> 42:57.470
Just a little more,

42:58.280 --> 43:00.110
and his mental defenses
would have been broken.

43:00.110 --> 43:01.230
Think about it.

43:02.150 --> 43:03.480
Someone who can get a gun

43:04.030 --> 43:05.320
couldn't be a nobody, could they?
